{"title":"Combined feed","url":"https://Vinnl.github.io/feeds/all.xml","elements":[{"title":"Wangdue Phodrang Dzong (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that the <b><a href=\"/wiki/Wangdue_Phodrang_Dzong\" title=\"Wangdue Phodrang Dzong\">Wangdue Phodrang Dzong</a></b> <i>(pictured)</i> was destroyed by a fire in 1837, damaged by an earthquake in 1897 and destroyed again by a fire in 2012?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wangdue_Phodrang_Dzong","retrieved":1781776458919},{"title":"Bahu Begum (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that <b><a href=\"/wiki/Bahu_Begum\" title=\"Bahu Begum\">Bahu Begum</a></b> gave up her nose ring with pearls for her husband's sovereignty?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bahu_Begum","retrieved":1781776458919},{"title":"49,XXYYY syndrome (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that <a href=\"/wiki/Dysmorphic_feature\" title=\"Dysmorphic feature\">facial dysmorphism</a> and moderate <a href=\"/wiki/Intellectual_disability\" title=\"Intellectual disability\">intellectual disability</a> are symptoms of <b><a href=\"/wiki/XXYYY_syndrome\" title=\"XXYYY syndrome\">49,XXYYY syndrome</a></b>?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/XXYYY_syndrome","retrieved":1781776458920},{"title":"Walt Whitman Park (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that <b><a href=\"/wiki/Walt_Whitman_Park_(Washington,_D.C.)\" title=\"Walt Whitman Park (Washington, D.C.)\">Walt Whitman Park</a></b> was the site of the first playground built on public parkland for children of U.S. government workers?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Walt_Whitman_Park_(Washington,_D.C.)","retrieved":1781776458930},{"title":"Trickcal: Chibi Go (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that the original <i><b><a href=\"/wiki/Trickcal:_Chibi_Go\" title=\"Trickcal: Chibi Go\">Trickcal: Chibi Go</a></b></i> shut down only two hours after it was released?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Trickcal:_Chibi_Go","retrieved":1781776458954},{"title":"Alec Radford (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that in 2018, <b><a href=\"/wiki/Alec_Radford\" title=\"Alec Radford\">Alec Radford</a></b> was the lead author on OpenAI's research paper on <a href=\"/wiki/Generative_pre-trained_transformer\" title=\"Generative pre-trained transformer\">generative pre-trained transformers</a>, which form the foundation of ChatGPT?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alec_Radford","retrieved":1781776458954},{"title":"Children of the Sun (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that the Jay Chou album <i><b><a href=\"/wiki/Children_of_the_Sun_(Jay_Chou_album)\" title=\"Children of the Sun (Jay Chou album)\">Children of the Sun</a></b></i> was named after a note he got with a box of mangoes?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Children_of_the_Sun_(Jay_Chou_album)","retrieved":1781776458957},{"title":"Jan Djong (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that <b><a href=\"/wiki/Jan_Djong\" title=\"Jan Djong\">Jan Djong</a></b> was fired from his post one day after his supporters held a demonstration in his support?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jan_Djong","retrieved":1781776458957},{"title":"It Takes Two (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that <a href=\"/wiki/Take-Two_Interactive\" title=\"Take-Two Interactive\">Take-Two Interactive</a> filed a trademark claim against <i><b><a href=\"/wiki/It_Takes_Two_(video_game)\" title=\"It Takes Two (video game)\">It Takes Two</a></b></i><span style=\"padding-left:0.15em;\">?</span>","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/It_Takes_Two_(video_game)","retrieved":1781776458958},{"title":"Destination of the Month (Wikivoyage recommendations)","contents":"<span class=\"mw-empty-elt\" about=\"#mwt8\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\" id=\"mwIQ\" data-mw=\"{&quot;parts&quot;:[{&quot;template&quot;:{&quot;target&quot;:{&quot;wt&quot;:&quot;banner&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:&quot;./Template:Banner&quot;},&quot;params&quot;:{&quot;direction&quot;:{&quot;wt&quot;:&quot;left&quot;